{"tid":1887981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［數學家］湖北省健康委員會：全省新增確診病例349宗；其中，武漢市有615宗","createTime":"2020-02-20T02:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T05:23:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63747758c30d96a947bc2a57fed83b2529abab80","tid":1887981,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37UQUcz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37UQUcz.png&h=9f356413&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puXnLjf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuXnLjf.png&h=060d14f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖北省衛健委公布，全省新增新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診病例349例，不過，單是武漢市卻有615例，超出全省數字。<br />\n<br />\n湖北省於本月13日公布，把臨床診斷病例納入確診病例，導致單日湖北的確診數字在12日創新高達14840例。不過，不到一星期，當局又改變決策，再次調整通報準則，17日公布的16日的確診數字不再列入新增臨床診斷病例數。<br />\n<br />\n於19日，全省新增病亡108例，其中武漢市88例。<br />\n<br />\n全省新增出院1209例，其中：武漢市553例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-349-%E4%BE%8B-%E5%96%AE%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-615-%E4%BE%8B-%E8%B6%85%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%9C%81%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-349-%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2-615-%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%2F&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5PDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=f21496cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-349-%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2-615-%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25B6